title: EaseUS Partition Master Technician v10.8 Multilang [deepstatus]
description:
EaseUS Partition Master Technician v10.8 Multilang [deepstatus]

EaseUS Partition Master is an ALL-IN-ONE partition solution and disk
management software, which includes three main functions:
Partition Manager, Disk & Partition Copy Wizard, Partition Recovery
Wizard, with hardware RAID support.

Languages:
English, German, Spanish, French, Portuguese, Polish, Japanese.

Support Windows 10/8/7/Vista/XP



[INSTALLATION]



- Unpack, install the application.

- Block <installation dir>binMain.exe in your firewall, to enable
offline activation and prevent your license from getting
blacklisted.

- Use Keygen to generate a license code and paste it in the
activation dialog.

- Copy the machine code and paste it in our Keygen.
Paste the generated activation code back in the activation dialog.

- Ok, It's Activated!
